Package: rpathsonpaths
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Population Genetics of Food-borne Diseases
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Martin", "Hinsch", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="hinsch.martin@gmail.com"),
			person("Thibaut", "Jombart", role=c("ctb")))
Description: A population genetics simulator for food-borne diseases. It 
	provides methods to simulate the spread of pathogens on a food transport network and the 
	resulting genetic structure of an outbreak.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: methods, utils, Rcpp (>= 0.12.9)
Suggests: igraph, knitr, rmarkdown, testthat, outbreaks, epicontacts, gtools
LinkingTo: Rcpp, BH
SystemRequirements: C++11
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/mhinsch/rpathsonpaths
BugReports: https://github.com/mhinsch/rpathsonpaths/issues

